===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}

{{Han compound|斤|車|ls=ic|c1=s|c2=s|t1=axe|t2=cart; vehicle}}. It refers to an ancient punishment in which a body was torn apart using carts, and by extension, conveys the meaning “to cut.” Another theory expresses the idea of cutting wood to make a vehicle.<ref>Digital Shinjigen 2017</ref>

